###############################################################################
# DESIGN PRINCIPLES
###############################################################################
Glass/Glow Aesthetic:
  - Surfaces: Semi-transparent with backdrop blur
  - Depth: Created via layered shadows and glows
  - Motion: Subtle, purposeful animations (pulse, glow)
  - Colors: Primary green (hsl(74 60% 44%)) with theme variants
  - Accessibility: All effects have reduced-motion fallbacks

Token Organization:
  - Base tokens: colors, spacing, typography
  - Semantic tokens: glass-*, primary, destructive
  - Component tokens: specific to components
  - Theme tokens: light/dark mode variants

